*cinnamon-2.8.4-r1 (17 Nov 2015)

  17 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -cinnamon-2.8.4.ebuild,
  +cinnamon-2.8.4-r1.ebuild, +files/cinnamon-2.8.4-path-is-symlink.patch:
  2.8.4: Support /usr/lib symlink

   /usr/lib can be a symlink on Gentoo systems.
  This commit fixes to support /usr/lib symlink.
   See https://github.com/linuxmint/Cinnamon/issues/4767

  17 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> cinnamon-2.8.4.ebuild:
  Update cinnamon components version to 2.8

